Oil, Gas and Consumable Fuels

Company Overview of Illinois Power Fuels and Services Company



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Illinois Power Fuels and Services Company supplies coal, natural gas, and oil to its parent company Ameren Energy Resources Company, LLC and its affiliated operating companies. In addition, it provides ash management and emission services for 12,000 megawatts of generating capacity. The company was formerly known as Ameren Energy Fuels and Services Company. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is based in Houston, Texas. Illinois Power Fuels and Services Company operates as a subsidiary of Ameren Energy Resources Company, LLC.


