            Sunrise Ag Service Company is a locally owned and operated agricultural cooperative that serves farmers and homeowners throughout Illinois. The company offers a variety of products and services for agricultural farms, lawns and gardens. Its products include a range of fertilizers, seeds, lubricants, greases and power fuels. Sunrise Ag Service Company also offers customized application and processing services. The company additionally offers direct marketing services for grains and other products. Additionally, it owns and operates Country Plaza Farm and Home store, which provides Carhartt and walls clothes, rocky boots, farm and plumbing supplies, power hand tools and electrical equipment. Sunrise Ag Service Company also offers various automotive services, such as oil changes and wheel alignment, as well as shock, brakes and small engine repair. The company maintains one of its locations in Virginia, Ill.
          






















